rComments: Vitaly is by far the best teaching assistant I have ever had.  His explanation and detail on subjects really brings his audience to examine the material more closely and therefore bringing more interest into the very dry subject of functional histology. I wish he taught more classes because I would definitely take them.

Vitaly is so great! He made the class fun, interesting, and he is so knowledgeable about the topic. It really helps having a teacher who not only understands the material but is also passionate about what he does and the students he works with. I wish he could teach all my classes! Not to mention...he's not bad to look at either ;)
Great class...not too stressful.  Tells you exactly what you need to know.
One of the best TA's/teachers that I have ever had.  Cares about the students and wants us to learn and succeed.
